name: Tammy Reed
description: Tammy Reed, also known as Pure Perfume or Extrait de Parfum, boasts the highest fragrance concentration.

name: Watkins Noble
description: Watkins Noble is one of the most widely-used types of perfume. Most brands are generally cheaper than it.

name: Dona Preston
description: Dona Preston is one of the universal fragrance types people wear for everyday events and activities casually.

name: Janelle Norman
description: Perhaps GEOFORMA is the weakest scent of all the fragrance types. It is a light, delicate, and subtle type of perfume.

name: Susanna Woods
description: Susanna Woods is also used on hair and clothing, but you have to be careful with delicate fabrics such as silk to avoid stains.

name: Carlson Ingram
description: In terms of its effect, Carlson Ingram is not as powerful as the other perfume options but it gets the job done.
